text: Erny Brenner (13 September 1931 - 9 July 2016)"Erny Brenner am Samstag verstorben." tageblatt.lu, 2016-07-12. was a Luxembourgian association football player. He was a member of the Luxembourg national football team from 1955 to 1965. He was born in Dudelange, Luxembourg. Brenner died on 9 July 2016 in Esch-sur-Alzette, Luxembourg, aged 84. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Luxembourgian footballers
